metadata.name: Bathing in the Neon Rain
metadata.description:
I'm admiring the neon rain. From the night haze of the sky, glowing threads fall on me. Splashes fly, colored waves caress the skin. And it seems that I am in the middle of a fireworks display, which envelops me with its warmth and energy.

Photos from my photo shoot were used as a reference. 
Size 2000x3000 px
On request I can send 2667x4000 px
